safetyTips: Hand Covers, and Anti Bacterial Products used in Kitchen
name: STREET KINGS SMOKE SHACK
address: Coachworks Yard, Ashford, Dover Place, TN23 1HU
description: American smoked BBQ joint in the revamped Coachworks Yard, all our food is home made and smoked on site. We serve Brisket, Pulled Pork, Ribs, Chicken, Turkey & a smoked Link.  Served with Mac & Cheese, Rice & Peas, Homemade Slaw, and Potato salad. We offer eat in or collection, our opening hours are  Friday 12-11, Saturday 12-11 and Sunday 12-6.
